Installation
------------

1\) get installation image 2) unsquashfs nix store 3) locate and edit
init 3.a) remove upstart 3.b) locate and start bash from init 3.c) copy
/etc/resolve.conf to installation medium 4) chroot into installation
medium 5) follow NixOS installation manual 6) edit configuratio.nix
(howto incorporate information above) 8) nixos-checkout 7) perform
nixos-install ...

